attr.title: SokoFrog
attr.desc: SokoFrog is a puzzle game about pushing boxes, help your frog friend get to the next level.
attr.inst:
Instructions: Purchase the game from steam. Download the game. 
Place all the game files into ports/sokofrog/assets
